WEBVTT

1
00:39:02.730 --> 00:39:07.780 
时间流逝得越来越快
The days, weeks, months go by more quickly.

2
00:39:07.880 --> 00:39:10.740 
那么一天  一年
What does a day or a year...

3
00:39:11.680 --> 00:39:13.940 
或者一个世纪  对你来说意味着什么
or a century mean to you?

4
00:39:13.940 --> 00:39:15.980 
生死轮转呢
The birth-death cycle?

5
00:39:16.230 --> 00:39:17.440 
动荡
Turbulence.

6
00:39:17.840 --> 00:39:18.920 
我遇到某个人
I meet someone,

7
00:39:19.580 --> 00:39:22.060 
知道了他的名字  说了几句话  然后他就死了
Learn their name, say a word, they're gone.

8
00:39:22.350 --> 00:39:26.610 
其他人就像海浪  潮来潮去
Others come like waves. Rise, fall.

9
00:39:28.180 --> 00:39:30.580 
又像麦浪  随风飘拂
Ripples in a wheat field, blown by the wind.

10
00:39:30.780 --> 00:39:32.740 
你就没感觉到累过吗
Do you ever get tired of it all?

